# Task 2: Customer Segmentation Using Unsupervised Learning

## Objective
Cluster customers based on spending habits and propose marketing strategies tailored to each segment.

## Dataset
Mall Customers Dataset

## Approach
- Conducted EDA to understand distributions and relationships
- Standardized numeric features
- Applied K-Means clustering
- Selected optimal number of clusters using Elbow + Silhouette score
- Visualized clusters using PCA (2D)
- Proposed marketing strategies for each cluster based on their behavioral profile

